[Holder, PRegex, current, plus, classify](extension-layout-boundary-lib.ssc)

# Imported extension use

```scalascript
val holder = Holder(20)
println(holder.current)
println(holder.plus(2))
println(classify(PRegex("rx"), "no"))
println(classify(Holder(0), "fallback"))
```
